[SPEAKER_02] Uskrsni.

936
00:34:41,320 --> 00:34:43,340
[SPEAKER_02] Znači Isu se uskrsne,

937
00:34:43,340 --> 00:34:44,500
[SPEAKER_02] uskrsni i ti čovječe.

938
00:34:44,500 --> 00:34:45,480
[SPEAKER_02] Uskrsni u duhu,

939
00:34:45,480 --> 00:34:46,460
[SPEAKER_02] uskrsni u srcu,

940
00:34:46,460 --> 00:34:48,059
[SPEAKER_02] uskrsni u vjeru,

941
00:34:48,059 --> 00:34:48,539
[SPEAKER_02] u nadi,

942
00:34:48,539 --> 00:34:49,800
[SPEAKER_02] vjeruj ono,

943
00:34:49,800 --> 00:34:50,599
[SPEAKER_02] budi radostan,

944
00:34:50,599 --> 00:34:51,800
[SPEAKER_02] živi punim plučima,

945
00:34:51,800 --> 00:34:54,659
[SPEAKER_02] raduj se jer gospodin je živ,

946
00:34:54,659 --> 00:34:55,460
[SPEAKER_02] nisi siročen,

947
00:34:55,460 --> 00:34:56,360
[SPEAKER_02] nisi ostavljen,

948
00:34:56,360 --> 00:34:57,920
[SPEAKER_02] meni je to najljepše ono.

949
00:34:58,940 --> 00:35:00,719
[SPEAKER_02] To bi ono poželio svima

950
00:35:00,719 --> 00:35:02,719
[SPEAKER_02] jer kažem da i mi uskrsnemo

951
00:35:02,719 --> 00:35:03,960
[SPEAKER_02] u duhu zajedno sa Isusom

952
00:35:03,960 --> 00:35:06,199
[SPEAKER_02] da osjetimo tu milost

953
00:35:06,199 --> 00:35:08,000
[SPEAKER_02] i živu vjeru i nadu.

954
00:35:08,000 --> 00:35:09,099
[SPEAKER_02] To je najbolje.

955
00:35:09,099 --> 00:35:11,059
[SPEAKER_00] Rekla sam,

956
00:35:11,059 --> 00:35:12,300
[SPEAKER_00] Antunovski hodimate

957
00:35:12,300 --> 00:35:13,619
[SPEAKER_00] u šestom mjesecu,

958
00:35:13,619 --> 00:35:15,380
[SPEAKER_00] sedmog šestog,

959
00:35:15,380 --> 00:35:15,880
[SPEAKER_00] je li tako?

960
00:35:15,880 --> 00:35:17,619
[SPEAKER_00] To nije zapravo shodočešće,

961
00:35:17,619 --> 00:35:19,699
[SPEAKER_00] nego kažu put vjere mladih.

962
00:35:19,699 --> 00:35:21,719
[SPEAKER_00] Prošle godine je bio super,

963
00:35:21,719 --> 00:35:22,320
[SPEAKER_00] odličan.

964
00:35:22,320 --> 00:35:23,599
[SPEAKER_00] Koliko je ono bilo mladih ljudi?

965
00:35:23,599 --> 00:35:25,260
[SPEAKER_02] Ja mislim da je prošle godine

966
00:35:25,260 --> 00:35:26,900
[SPEAKER_02] na završnici bilo oko 15.000,

967
00:35:26,900 --> 00:35:28,800
[SPEAKER_02] ove godine čekujemo puno više.

968
00:35:28,940 --> 00:35:29,960
[SPEAKER_02] Krenuli smo ozbiljno,

969
00:35:29,960 --> 00:35:30,659
[SPEAKER_02] imamo puno...

970
00:35:30,659 --> 00:35:31,460
[SPEAKER_00] Za one koji ne znaju,

971
00:35:31,460 --> 00:35:32,280
[SPEAKER_00] samo ćemo reći,

972
00:35:32,280 --> 00:35:33,760
[SPEAKER_00] krećete od...

973
00:35:33,760 --> 00:35:34,679
[SPEAKER_02] Dakle, mi krećemo

974
00:35:34,679 --> 00:35:35,679
[SPEAKER_02] od srskih sela,

975
00:35:35,679 --> 00:35:37,860
[SPEAKER_02] pred programom u 11 sati,

976
00:35:37,860 --> 00:35:40,000
[SPEAKER_02] zatim to je slavljenje

977
00:35:40,000 --> 00:35:41,360
[SPEAKER_02] i animiraju mladi.

978
00:35:41,360 --> 00:35:42,780
[SPEAKER_02] U 12 sati je Sveta Misa

979
00:35:42,780 --> 00:35:44,340
[SPEAKER_02] i nakon Sveta Misa krećemo

980
00:35:44,340 --> 00:35:47,480
[SPEAKER_02] prema drugom dijelu grada,

981
00:35:47,480 --> 00:35:49,699
[SPEAKER_02] to je konkretno našem svetištu

982
00:35:49,699 --> 00:35:50,559
[SPEAKER_02] na Svetome Duhu,

983
00:35:50,559 --> 00:35:51,460
[SPEAKER_02] Svetom Antunu.

984
00:35:51,460 --> 00:35:54,300
[SPEAKER_02] Ali između toga imamo etape

985
00:35:54,300 --> 00:35:54,980
[SPEAKER_02] gdje stajemo.

986
00:35:54,980 --> 00:35:56,340
[SPEAKER_02] Prva je u Dubravi,

987
00:35:56,340 --> 00:35:57,559
[SPEAKER_02] kod Heslagočkih fratara,

988
00:35:57,559 --> 00:35:58,780
[SPEAKER_02] gdje ćemo imati molitvu,

989
00:35:58,780 --> 00:35:59,519
[SPEAKER_02] okrepu

990
00:35:59,519 --> 00:36:02,139
[SPEAKER_02] i onda idemo prema onom centralnom dijelu

991
00:36:02,139 --> 00:36:03,139
[SPEAKER_02] gdje je evangelizacija

992
00:36:03,139 --> 00:36:03,780
[SPEAKER_02] na trgu Bana Jelačića,

993
00:36:03,780 --> 00:36:07,039
[SPEAKER_02] gdje će biti podignuta velika pozornica

994
00:36:07,039 --> 00:36:08,840
[SPEAKER_02] i gdje će biti molitva,

995
00:36:08,840 --> 00:36:09,579
[SPEAKER_02] slavljenje,

996
00:36:09,579 --> 00:36:10,760
[SPEAKER_02] jedan performans

997
00:36:10,760 --> 00:36:13,940
[SPEAKER_02] i tako evangelizacijskog karaktera.

998
00:36:13,940 --> 00:36:16,500
[SPEAKER_02] Nakon trga krećemo dalje

999
00:36:16,500 --> 00:36:17,760
[SPEAKER_02] naš put prema Bazilici

1000
00:36:17,760 --> 00:36:19,179
[SPEAKER_02] gdje imamo klanjenje,

1001
00:36:19,179 --> 00:36:20,599
[SPEAKER_02] slavljenje i druženje.

1002
00:36:20,599 --> 00:36:22,659
[SPEAKER_02] Evo, to je ta nekakva ruta,

1003
00:36:22,659 --> 00:36:23,699
[SPEAKER_02] ali ja uvijek govorim

1004
00:36:23,699 --> 00:36:25,860
[SPEAKER_02] da ovo nije prazan hod.

1005
00:36:25,860 --> 00:36:28,300
[SPEAKER_02] Mi već puno, puno vremena

1006
00:36:28,300 --> 00:36:29,719
[SPEAKER_02] molimo za tu nakanu,

1007
00:36:29,719 --> 00:36:31,659
[SPEAKER_02] pripremamo se što tehnički,

1008
00:36:31,659 --> 00:36:32,659
[SPEAKER_02] što duhovno,

1009
00:36:32,659 --> 00:36:33,880
[SPEAKER_02] jer nama je u interesu

1010
00:36:33,880 --> 00:36:34,860
[SPEAKER_02] da svi ljudi koji dožive

1011
00:36:34,860 --> 00:36:35,739
[SPEAKER_02] zaista dođu,

1012
00:36:35,739 --> 00:36:37,019
[SPEAKER_02] dožive duhovnu obnovu,

1013
00:36:37,039 --> 00:36:38,820
[SPEAKER_02] dožive zajedništvo, ponos

1014
00:36:38,820 --> 00:36:40,739
[SPEAKER_02] i to je ono što mladi najviše ističe.

1015
00:36:40,739 --> 00:36:41,860
[SPEAKER_02] Mi ovi dana smo počeli

1016
00:36:41,860 --> 00:36:42,699
[SPEAKER_02] na društvenim mrežama

1017
00:36:42,699 --> 00:36:45,219
[SPEAKER_02] objavljivati isječke snimke

1018
00:36:45,219 --> 00:36:47,539
[SPEAKER_02] zapravo sudionika

1019
00:36:47,539 --> 00:36:49,159
[SPEAKER_02] prošlogodišnjih sahoda

1020
00:36:49,159 --> 00:36:50,679
[SPEAKER_02] koji su dali svoje svjedočanstva

1021
00:36:50,679 --> 00:36:52,199
[SPEAKER_02] kak je bilo

1022
00:36:52,199 --> 00:36:53,760
[SPEAKER_02] i što su oni kako su to doživjeli.

1023
00:36:53,760 --> 00:36:55,420
[SPEAKER_02] Tako da ljudi ovi sami mogu čuti

1024
00:36:55,420 --> 00:36:57,460
[SPEAKER_02] što mogu očekivati

1025
00:36:57,460 --> 00:36:58,760
[SPEAKER_02] ako dođu.

1026
00:36:58,760 --> 00:37:00,420
[SPEAKER_02] Ja ovim putem pozivam svih,

1027
00:37:00,420 --> 00:37:02,460
[SPEAKER_02] jer zaista sam ponosan

1028
00:37:02,460 --> 00:37:04,139
[SPEAKER_02] da ovo više nije hrvatski,

1029
00:37:04,139 --> 00:37:04,940
[SPEAKER_02] nije nacionalni.

1030
00:37:04,940 --> 00:37:06,820
[SPEAKER_02] Prvo smo išli u okvirima Zagreba,

1031
00:37:06,820 --> 00:37:08,800
[SPEAKER_02] pa smo iskočili iz toga na nacionalni.

1032
00:37:08,800 --> 00:37:10,539
[SPEAKER_02] Sad je internacionalni,

1033
00:37:10,539 --> 00:37:12,519
[SPEAKER_02] jer nam dolaze sa svih strana,

1034
00:37:12,519 --> 00:37:13,619
[SPEAKER_02] čak se uključuju, kažem,

1035
00:37:13,619 --> 00:37:14,920
[SPEAKER_02] prošle godine je Bila i Makedonija,

1036
00:37:14,920 --> 00:37:15,900
[SPEAKER_02] i Bosna i Srbija,

1037
00:37:15,900 --> 00:37:19,280
[SPEAKER_02] i ove susjedne zemlje Slovenija

1038
00:37:19,280 --> 00:37:20,139
[SPEAKER_02] i ostali.

1039
00:37:20,139 --> 00:37:21,440
[SPEAKER_02] Ali naši, naravno,

1040
00:37:21,440 --> 00:37:22,880
[SPEAKER_02] Hrvati koji žive u dijaspori,

1041
00:37:22,880 --> 00:37:24,500
[SPEAKER_02] dosta njih organizirano dolazi

1042
00:37:24,500 --> 00:37:26,340
[SPEAKER_02] autobusima i to mi je nekako

1043
00:37:26,340 --> 00:37:27,420
[SPEAKER_02] baš prekrasno vidjeti

1044
00:37:27,420 --> 00:37:30,219
[SPEAKER_02] da će se okupiti ta naša mladež

1045
00:37:30,219 --> 00:37:31,599
[SPEAKER_02] još jednom u Zagrebu,

1046
00:37:31,599 --> 00:37:33,539
[SPEAKER_02] još jače, još više.

1047
00:37:33,539 --> 00:37:35,940
[SPEAKER_02] I baš vidim jedan interes ogroman ko njih.

1048
00:37:35,940 --> 00:37:37,079
[SPEAKER_00] A prekrasno je zapravo vidjeti

1049
00:37:37,079 --> 00:37:38,420
[SPEAKER_00] mlade nasmijane ljude

1050
00:37:38,420 --> 00:37:39,880
[SPEAKER_00] koji pjevaju i slave Boga.

1051
00:37:39,880 --> 00:37:41,199
[SPEAKER_02] E pa to je svjedočanstvo,

1052
00:37:41,199 --> 00:37:41,820
[SPEAKER_02] to je radost,

1053
00:37:41,820 --> 00:37:42,659
[SPEAKER_02] to je živi Bog.

1054
00:37:43,599 --> 00:37:45,619
[SPEAKER_00] Zaplaćate li onda od sreće kad to...

1055
00:37:45,619 --> 00:37:47,300
[SPEAKER_02] Naravno, da me emocije udare

1056
00:37:47,300 --> 00:37:49,079
[SPEAKER_02] i da kad vidim što u mladosti...

1057
00:37:49,079 --> 00:37:50,420
[SPEAKER_02] Dobri, jako organizator sam taj dan

1058
00:37:50,420 --> 00:37:51,219
[SPEAKER_02] dosta pod šokom,

1059
00:37:51,219 --> 00:37:52,940
[SPEAKER_02] ali me više dirne poslije

1060
00:37:52,940 --> 00:37:54,420
[SPEAKER_02] kad gledam te snimke

1061
00:37:54,420 --> 00:37:55,539
[SPEAKER_02] i to kad vidim kak je zapravo

1062
00:37:55,539 --> 00:37:56,300
[SPEAKER_02] realno bilo.

1063
00:37:56,300 --> 00:37:57,320
[SPEAKER_02] Ali se sjećam,

1064
00:37:57,320 --> 00:37:58,219
[SPEAKER_02] prošle godine je da je bilo

1065
00:37:58,219 --> 00:38:00,099
[SPEAKER_02] dvirljivo kada smo na trgu

1066
00:38:00,099 --> 00:38:00,900
[SPEAKER_02] imali molitvu,

1067
00:38:00,900 --> 00:38:01,840
[SPEAKER_02] svi su kleklili

1068
00:38:01,840 --> 00:38:03,300
[SPEAKER_02] i je nastala ta tišina

1069
00:38:03,300 --> 00:38:04,420
[SPEAKER_02] i kada je počela molitva.

1070
00:38:04,420 --> 00:38:05,280
[SPEAKER_02] Bože, kako...

1071
00:38:05,280 --> 00:38:06,380
[SPEAKER_02] Ja mislim da nije bilo osobe

1072
00:38:06,380 --> 00:38:07,300
[SPEAKER_02] koja tamo nije plakala.

1073
00:38:07,300 --> 00:38:08,659
[SPEAKER_02] I onda kad smo ustali,

1074
00:38:13,599 --> 00:38:14,280
[SPEAKER_02] sad naglašava ovo

1075
00:38:14,280 --> 00:38:15,440
[SPEAKER_02] da mi jako puno molimo

1076
00:38:15,440 --> 00:38:16,920
[SPEAKER_02] jer mi taj dan samo gledamo

1077
00:38:16,920 --> 00:38:17,860
[SPEAKER_02] što smo molili.

1078
00:38:17,860 --> 00:38:19,800
[SPEAKER_02] Dakle, nema taj dan više ništa,

1079
00:38:19,800 --> 00:38:22,000
[SPEAKER_02] nego taj dan se samo milost spušta.

1080
00:38:22,000 --> 00:38:23,059
[SPEAKER_02] Što smo nam molili,

1081
00:38:23,059 --> 00:38:23,860
[SPEAKER_02] to se i događa.

1082
00:38:23,860 --> 00:38:26,000
[SPEAKER_00] A kako se ta milost može

1083
00:38:26,000 --> 00:38:28,139
[SPEAKER_00] fra Stjepane na kraju spustiti

1084
00:38:28,139 --> 00:38:30,539
[SPEAKER_00] na svakogodnost?

1085
00:38:30,539 --> 00:38:32,539
[SPEAKER_00] Ne samo ova vaša sa hodučešća

1086
00:38:32,539 --> 00:38:34,159
[SPEAKER_00] koja će biti ove godine

1087
00:38:34,159 --> 00:38:35,480
[SPEAKER_00] 7.6.

1088
00:38:35,480 --> 00:38:37,340
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, svi se prijavite.

1089
00:38:37,340 --> 00:38:38,940
[SPEAKER_00] I dalje tražite

1090
00:38:38,940 --> 00:38:41,739
[SPEAKER_00] one bodyguardove, čuvare...

1091
00:38:41,739 --> 00:38:43,579
[SPEAKER_02] Dakle, samo tražimo još bubnjare.

1092
00:38:43,599 --> 00:38:44,500
[SPEAKER_02] Sve drugo imamo već.

1093
00:38:44,500 --> 00:38:45,019
[SPEAKER_02] Ozbiljno?

1094
00:38:45,019 --> 00:38:46,400
[SPEAKER_02] Ove godine ste puno brže.

1095
00:38:46,400 --> 00:38:50,099
[SPEAKER_02] 120 redara, 75 sestara prve pomoći.

1096
00:38:50,099 --> 00:38:52,599
[SPEAKER_02] Dakle, svi drugi samo ako još bubnjara ima,

1097
00:38:52,599 --> 00:38:54,219
[SPEAKER_02] to će nam dobro doći.

1098
00:38:54,219 --> 00:38:57,179
[SPEAKER_00] Ok, to mi je prekrasno začuti.

1099
00:38:57,179 --> 00:38:59,719
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, na kraju, milost Božju,

1100
00:38:59,719 --> 00:39:02,179
[SPEAKER_00] kako spustiti na nas,

1101
00:39:02,179 --> 00:39:04,059
[SPEAKER_00] na pojedinca, na naše obitelji,

1102
00:39:04,059 --> 00:39:05,860
[SPEAKER_00] na našu domovinu, na svijet?

1103
00:39:05,860 --> 00:39:07,699
[SPEAKER_02] Nismo pričali da li može,

1104
00:39:07,699 --> 00:39:10,099
[SPEAKER_02] ali kad mi postavljaš pitanje

1105
00:39:10,099 --> 00:39:11,500
[SPEAKER_02] kako spustiti, pa molitvom.

1106
00:39:11,500 --> 00:39:14,460
[SPEAKER_02] pa ja bi se onda pomolio za vas

1107
00:39:14,460 --> 00:39:15,760
[SPEAKER_02] i za one koji će gledati ovaj video.

1108
00:39:15,760 --> 00:39:16,559
[SPEAKER_00] Ko će molim?

1109
00:39:16,559 --> 00:39:17,079
[SPEAKER_02] Može.

1110
00:39:17,079 --> 00:39:20,780
[SPEAKER_02] Dobri Bože,

1111
00:39:20,780 --> 00:39:23,199
[SPEAKER_02] hvala ti na ovom trenutku milosti.

1112
00:39:23,199 --> 00:39:25,639
[SPEAKER_02] Hvala ti na daru svake osobe

1113
00:39:25,639 --> 00:39:27,699
[SPEAKER_02] što si je stvorio tako kakva jest.

1114
00:39:28,800 --> 00:39:29,699
[SPEAKER_02] Molim te, gospodine,

1115
00:39:29,699 --> 00:39:31,599
[SPEAKER_02] ti si nas iz ljubavi stvorio

1116
00:39:31,599 --> 00:39:33,360
[SPEAKER_02] i postavio ovaj svijet.

1117
00:39:33,360 --> 00:39:35,719
[SPEAKER_02] Nekoga da bude svečenik,

1118
00:39:35,719 --> 00:39:37,519
[SPEAKER_02] nekoga majka, otac, dijete.

1119
00:39:37,519 --> 00:39:39,940
[SPEAKER_02] Blagoslovi nas Isuse snagom

1120
00:39:39,940 --> 00:39:40,780
[SPEAKER_02] duha svetoga,

1121
00:39:40,780 --> 00:39:42,139
[SPEAKER_02] ti koji si ju skrsnuo.

1122
00:39:42,139 --> 00:39:44,099
[SPEAKER_02] Neka vatra duha svetoga

1123
00:39:44,099 --> 00:39:45,039
[SPEAKER_02] siđe i na nas.

1124
00:39:45,039 --> 00:39:46,960
[SPEAKER_02] Neka mać duha svetoga

1125
00:39:46,960 --> 00:39:48,739
[SPEAKER_02] odagna od nas svaku tjeskobu,

1126
00:39:48,739 --> 00:39:50,579
[SPEAKER_02] strah, sumnju, depresiju,

1127
00:39:50,579 --> 00:39:52,059
[SPEAKER_02] svaku krizu.

1128
00:39:52,860 --> 00:39:53,920
[SPEAKER_02] Milošću duha svetoga

1129
00:39:53,920 --> 00:39:55,340
[SPEAKER_02] odmnovi naše obitelji.

1130
00:39:55,340 --> 00:39:57,579
[SPEAKER_02] Neka zavlada mir, ljubav.

1131
00:39:57,579 --> 00:39:59,139
[SPEAKER_02] Molimo te, Isuse,

1132
00:39:59,139 --> 00:40:01,119
[SPEAKER_02] svojom ljubavlju izliječi

1133
00:40:01,119 --> 00:40:02,000
[SPEAKER_02] sve naše rane,

1134
00:40:02,000 --> 00:40:04,360
[SPEAKER_02] rane koje smo nanijeli jedni drugima.

1135
00:40:04,360 --> 00:40:06,039
[SPEAKER_02] Izliječi, gospodine,

1136
00:40:06,039 --> 00:40:07,539
[SPEAKER_02] naše međuljudske odnose.

1137
00:40:07,539 --> 00:40:09,280
[SPEAKER_02] Daruj nam duh ljubavi.

1138
00:40:09,280 --> 00:40:10,920
[SPEAKER_02] Ljubavi da možemo ljubiti

1139
00:40:10,920 --> 00:40:12,019
[SPEAKER_02] i svoje neprijatelje.

